<li><a href="Wilan%C3%B3w_Palace#The_sundial" title="Wilanów Palace">Wilanów Palace Sundial</a>, created by <a href="Johannes_Hevelius" title="Johannes Hevelius">Johannes Hevelius</a> in about 1684.</li>
</ul>
